<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Payment Verification Issue - Origin Food House</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: #f44336; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0;">Payment Verification Issue</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 30px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hi {{ownerName}},</p>

    <p>We were unable to verify your payment for <strong>{{storeName}}</strong>.</p>

    <div style="background: #ffebee; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #f44336; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #c62828;">Payment Details:</h3>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Reference Number:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-family: monospace;">{{referenceNumber}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Tier:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{requestedTier}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Amount:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">${{amount}} USD</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; vertical-align: top;"><strong>Reason:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #d32f2f;">{{rejectionReason}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p><strong>What to do next:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Review the rejection reason above</li>
      <li>Ensure your payment was completed successfully</li>
      <li>Upload a clear, high-quality payment proof</li>
      <li>Verify the reference number matches your transfer</li>
      <li>If needed, contact our support team for assistance</li>
    </ol>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{uploadProofUrl}}" style="background: #f44336; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">
        Upload New Payment Proof
      </a>
    </p>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        <strong>Need Help?</strong> Contact our support team at support@originfoodhouse.com with your reference number.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
      We apologize for the inconvenience and are here to help resolve this quickly.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
    &copy; {{year}} Origin Food House. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>
</html>
